The evaluation of the developed algorithms using a simulation framework indicates a focus on system simulation and modeling (cs.SI). The optimization properties mentioned in the abstract suggest a focus on control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the use of programmed graph transformation suggests a focus on programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
